  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a sha256 content hash is present but the ed25519 digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending review-board approval. All 13 credibility factors are assessed or flagged. Decision: Accepted with conditions.",
