    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 (VAD hemolysis prediction at MRL 5) has been reviewed and conditionally accepted pending completion of the digital signature workflow. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated: 7 factors were formally assessed (all achieving levels below required levels for MRL 5), and 6 factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The package is submitted under the Minimal profile with a content hash (sha256) for integrity verification; the ed25519 digital signature is pending review-board countersignature and will be appended upon completion of the institutional signature workflow. The conditional acceptance acknowledges the identified credibility gaps and requires a gap-closure plan prior to regulatory submission.",
